This repository contains
1. Python script (bike_data_logger.py) to log data from the motion sensor to a Raspberry Pi.
        Logging begins automatically when Pi reboots.
2. Runtime Logs are timestamped and stored in Logs repository for debugging
3. Collected data is stored in bike_data_logs directory.
4. Script to stop logging process (stop.sh)
        Run ./stop.sh from the current directory
5. Script to manually start the logging process
        Run ./start.sh from the current direcory
6. Script to sync the logs to a remote Git repository
        Run ./sync.sh from the current directory.